    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note>Il <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arechi II</persName> offre
                            al monastero di S. Sofia di <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110"
                                >Benevento</placeName> (prosegue l'elenco iniziato con il doc.
                            3535):</note></ab>
                    <ab>(…) [9] Nec non et <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3408"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                                ><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> Sancti Archangeli</orgName> que
                        sita est in <geogName ref="#estates/3405"
                            key="#Gai #Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential"><rs
                                key="#Gai #Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential">gaio</rs> nostro
                                <placeName ref="#places/3416"
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Gai #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Condomae"
                                >Stoni</placeName></geogName>, et constituimus atque concessimus
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Condomae #Churches #Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Condomae #Churches #Monasteries"
                                >Sancte Sophie</rs></orgName> in ipso loco <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >corte</rs> et<rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Condomae #Slave_labour"
                            >condomas</rs> sex cum uxore et filiis suis et ex ipso gaio <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Size #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >territorium miliaria novem</rs>. (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
